{"tid":1571723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要反共就要比中國人更加大中華膠","createTime":"2019-09-15T13:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T15:52:43.000Z","uid":149496,"like":91,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"25f30be7f1218aa1bcfe7b9518f10149be336c1e","tid":1571723,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"經過呢幾個月 由反送中變成全民爭取民主 有樣野好明顯 就係一日共產黨唔倒台 香港都唔可能真正有民主 所以必須反共 要反共就一定要將革命燃燒到中國內部 咁就要同中國人connect<br />\n<br />\n中國有樣野好得意 就係 名不正則言不順 言不順則事不成<br />\n<br />\n共產黨無論做任何事都一定要站係道德高地 咁樣無論佢地做咩都係名正言順<br />\n<br />\n共產黨維穩最重要嘅工具之一就係民族主義 不論任何事 六四 香港 定中國國內反興建化工廠 垃圾焚化爐嘅示威 只要貼上外國勢力 別有用心 暴動等等嘅標籤 就可以打壓 就算好多對生活現況 對政府不滿嘅中國人都會因此支持中共<br />\n<br />\n中國嘅極端民族主義係共產黨嘅培養同鼓吹下根本無法改變 所以唔好幻想改變中國人 我地應該利用呢種民族主義 借力打力<br />\n<br />\n只要共產黨仍被視為係中國正當 正統 合法嘅政權 中國人都只會支持共產黨<br />\n任何人係咁嘅情況下反對共產黨只會被視為反對中國 分裂國家<br />\n<br />\n我地要為行動正名<br />\n<br />\n天無二日 民無二主 中國永遠只得一個 中國只可以有一個正當 正統嘅政權 呢個係中國人無法改變嘅思想<br />\n<br />\n所以我地反共一定要標榜自己做中國真正嘅繼承者 而將共產黨標籤為偽中華/偽中國 我地唔係要港獨 而係要恢復中華<br />\n<br />\n我地要發明一套思想黎否定共產黨政權嘅正統 同時表明我地係要建立真正嘅中華政權<br />\n<br />\n驅除馬列 恢復中華"},{"pid":"e164b89f78691968ac773f1bb1ca047ebf706851","tid":1571723,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"Translation: To be anti communist in China, we need to be more Chinese than the Chinese Communist party."},{"pid":"459fcb39e6b032bcfcb9e013518aa0ee758146ac","tid":1571723,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"我們需要critical thinking, 哲學，普世價值同埋non-aggression principle。 <br />\n<br />\nWhen you think about the recent events - government escalation of its aggression through police brutality, cruel and unusual punishments, manipulation of the legal system, we start to realise this is not only a problem with the CCP. This is a problem with the whole concept and nature of government itself.<br />\n<br />\nThe FIVE demands is a natural reaction to increased aggression from the governing classes in Beijing and Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nWhat Hong Kong people want, is a moral, free and open society with clear and fair rules, and a small government that stays out of people&rsquo;s lives. <br />\n<br />\nIn the long run, you want as little or no government because all monopolies on political Power and aggression corrupts. All governments eventually become out of control."},{"pid":"96b7fcc62247d349d671b8d35e3cb239e1a5103c","tid":1571723,"uid":292925,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"重現三民主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7127a793d91ea3fd9e4ea2bf93eed5f2424f122","tid":1571723,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d116d21ff98163f3dea97a44e1d48d142859defd","tid":1571723,"uid":264400,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔 到而家都未明對手係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續食燈籠玩月餅"},{"pid":"666d0e6dacebe8abe507dc145528dcd3883167c9","tid":1571723,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d116d21ff98163f3dea97a44e1d48d142859defd","tid":1571723,"uid":264400,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔 到而家都未明對手係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續食燈籠玩月餅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4764c4eb8ea73ce57a5894a6b03d7406348754","tid":1571723,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"十一應該遊行慶祝中華民國國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf12cc010950b78afd90bb70ba00db9ebb4f2fe8","tid":1571723,"uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0