By":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"困難在於好多內地人已經以為係中共令佢地今日咁發達<br />\n同埋民族興盛<br />\n<br />\n你點樣說服佢地中共唔係正統政權<br />\n有咩論點先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"政治:<br />\n1. 共產黨自稱寸土必爭 寸土不讓 但將150萬平方公里領土割讓予俄國 足足係41個台灣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-46120157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-46120157&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=b7ef8dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-46120157&h=b7517796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-46120157</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.open.com.hk/old_version/0808p20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.open.com.hk%2Fold_version%2F0808p20.html&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=6a39a923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.open.com.hk/old_version/0808p20.html</a><br />\n2. 政治腐敗 貪污成風 司法不公 百姓有冤無路訴 例子眾多 無需多言<br />\n<br />\n經濟:<br />\n1. 所謂共產黨領導下實現嘅經濟奇蹟完全係鳩吹出黎嘅<br />\n改革開放41年(1978-2019) 中國 2018 GDP per capita 係9500美元左右<br />\n日本戰後復甦40年(1945-1985) 日本 1985 GDP per capita 係11500美元<br />\n原來連架仔都比唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/publicdata/explore?ds=d5bncppjof8f9_&amp;met_y=ny_gdp_pcap_cd&amp;idim=country:JPN:USA:KOR&amp;hl=zh-Hant&amp;dl=zh-Hant#!ctype=l&amp;strail=false&amp;bcs=d&amp;nselm=h&amp;met_y=ny_gdp_pcap_cd&amp;scale_y=lin&amp;ind_y=false&amp;rdim=region&amp;idim=country:JPN:USA:KOR:HKG:CHN&amp;ifdim=region&amp;hl=zh_TW&amp;dl=en_US&amp;ind=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fpublicdata%2Fexplore%3Fds%3Dd5bncppjof8f9_%26met_y%3Dny_gdp_pcap_cd%26idim%3Dcountry%3AJPN%3AUSA%3AKOR%26hl%3Dzh-Hant%26dl%3Dzh-Hant%23%21ctype%3Dl%26strail%3Dfalse%26bcs%3Dd%26nselm%3Dh%26met_y%3Dny_gdp_pcap_cd%26scale_y%3Dlin%26ind_y%3Dfalse%26rdim%3Dregion%26idim%3Dcountry%3AJPN%3AUSA%3AKOR%3AHKG%3ACHN%26ifdim%3Dregion%26hl%3Dzh_TW%26dl%3Den_US%26ind%3Dfalse&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=83cf00da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/publicdata/explore?ds=d5bncppjof8f9_&amp;met_y=ny_gdp_pcap_cd&amp;idim=country:JPN:USA:KOR&amp;hl=zh-Hant&amp;dl=zh-Hant#!ctype=l&amp;strail=false&amp;bcs=d&amp;nselm=h&amp;met_y=ny_gdp_pcap_cd&amp;scale_y=lin&amp;ind_y=false&amp;rdim=region&amp;idim=country:JPN:USA:KOR:HKG:CHN&amp;ifdim=region&amp;hl=zh_TW&amp;dl=en_US&amp;ind=false</a><br />\n<br />\n我咁樣比較已經便宜左共產黨 如果由1949年開始到依家同依家嘅日本比 共產黨只會更無面<br />\n<br />\n2. 自稱社會主義國家 但貧富懸殊問題更甚於資本主義國家<br />\n<br />\n文化:<br />\n1. 香港人用繁體 中國人用簡體 唔洗多講<br />\n2. 粵語等南方方言更接近中古漢語 普通話係 漢兒盡作胡兒語 卻向城頭罵漢人<br />\n3. 如果有睇過共產黨嘅官方新聞稿 都會有&quot;全部都係中文字 隻隻都睇得明 但全部加埋一齊唔知up乜春&quot;嘅感覺 連官方都唔識得用中文<br />\n4. 中國人缺乏道德 原因之一在於中共建政初年嘅文化浩劫 文革 逼使好多文化人外逃 摧毀左中國嘅傳統文化 宗教思想 中國人缺乏道德同宗教約束 以致道德敗壞<br />\n香港人係英國殖民地 但比中國更似禮儀之邦"},{"pid":"43a22a37b74b54443a7b6bcd980cf2d7b83a974a","tid":1571723,"uid":308706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4764c4eb8ea73ce57a5894a6b03d7406348754","tid":1571723,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"十一應該遊行慶祝中華民國國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"燒黨旗就啱晒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6c3324df60fd77b5629abecbf3486490ac5d51","tid":1571723,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911a825e805ff8355ae9947924c258e093f3fd0f","tid":1571723,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"好似倪匡咁，我唔愛國使撚反共？"},{"pid":"c1f7ab843a83319bba53a068a7b66e046a679439","tid":1571723,"uid":271729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor